  "title": "*Up to $20/ Office hours* Locum Pharmacy Technician (Islandwide) #HCGT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Processes prescriptions and dispenses medications to patients</li><li>Supports Medication Delivery Service and PILBOX service for remote collection of medications</li><li>Provides Tele-dispensing services (where applicable)</li><li>Assists in video consultation and medication reconciliation</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>GCE ‘O’ Level with a Certificate in Pharmacy Technician Course (under MOH, PSS or its equivalent) or a Diploma in Pharmaceutical Science</li><li>Can take fresh Diploma or candidates with pharmacy technician experience</li></ul><p><br />All qualified applicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p>medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>",
